{"tid":2322013,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"深水埗弦雅開賣 投資者︰400幾萬買一伙收租","createTime":"2020-12-12T03:46:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T07:25:51.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2340ea1873513e03209f97beeaa51b56a32273a4","tid":2322013,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T03:46:47.000Z","msg":"弦雅今日早上10時起，於長沙灣喜薈商場開售53伙，準買家分批入場，有過百人出席，即場抽籤並揀樓。<br />\n準買家雷先生表示，預算以400幾萬買入弦雅單位，打算用作收租投資，是第一次在深水埗區投資。對於近期本港經濟環境轉壞，樓價輕微下跌，他認為因為項目銀碼比較細，不太擔心樓價問題。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201212/75EMO7Z7GNDDRKBYXU5XJRNF7I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201212%2F75EMO7Z7GNDDRKBYXU5XJRNF7I%2F&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jctVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=1ea44737\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201212%2F75EMO7Z7GNDDRKBYXU5XJRNF7I%2F&h=37e7813d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201212/75EMO7Z7GNDDRKBYXU5XJRNF7I/</a>"},{"pid":"3bef627ccbc73bba5a140f9ea9c204179bfcf1dc","tid":2322013,"uid":14918,"like":18,"dislike":3,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T03:51:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hxEspTr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhxEspTr.jpg&h=f24f7d33&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8664709a54d23ab66b6c6f9002196edb005d66cd","tid":2322013,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T03:57:30.000Z","msg":"深水埗通街道友露宿南亞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n賣2球都無興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97a4fbf93e20a6fe41a5604fd223e1c112cc33a9","tid":2322013,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T04:07:01.000Z","msg":"工都無得番 搵條撚租"},{"pid":"f88284fed9416ec3e1a4e09ff86070496d6e2b2d","t